---
// A margin note. On wide screens it floats into the right gutter; on narrow
// screens it becomes an indented, set-off block.
//
// Use in .astro files:   <Sidenote>Your aside here.</Sidenote>
// In markdown posts, use the equivalent raw HTML instead:
//   <aside class="sidenote">Your aside here.</aside>
//
// Either way, the *parent article* must carry the class "has-sidenotes"
// (PostLayout and NoteLayout already do) for the margin behaviour to kick in.
---
<aside class="sidenote"><slot /></aside>
